{"title":"De 'hypothetische' tijd","body":[{"type":"p","text":"De hypothetische tijd noemen we ook wel de 'onvoltooid verleden toekomende tijd' (o.v.t.t.)."},{"type":"p","text":"We gebruiken de o.v.t.t. voor hypothetische situaties. Op de volgende pagina wordt dit uitgelegd."},{"type":"p","text":"De o.v.t.t. werkt net zoals de toekomstige tijd, maar in plaats van de tegenwoordige tijd van van zullen gebruiken we de verleden tijd:"},{"type":"table","table":[["ik","zou + infinitive","we","zouden + infinitive"],["je","zou + infinitive","jullie","zouden + infinitive"],["hij","zou + infinitive","ze","zouden + infinitive"]]},{"type":"table","table":[["zeggen","stam: zeg","luisteren","stam: luister"],["ik","zou zeggen","ik","zou luisteren"],["jij","zou zeggen","je","zou luisteren"],["hij","zou zeggen","hij","zou luisteren"],["we","zouden zeggen","we","zouden luisteren"],["jullie","zouden zeggen","jullie","zouden luisteren"],["zij","zouden zeggen","ze","zouden luisteren"]]},{"type":"table","table":[["springen","stam: spring","betalen","stam: betaal"],["ik","zou springen","ik","zou betalen"],["jij","zou springen","je","zou betalen"],["hij","zou springen","hij","zou betalen"],["we","zouden springen","we","zouden betalen"],["jullie","zouden springen","jullie","zouden betalen"],["zij","zouden springen","ze","zouden betalen"]]},{"type":"p","text":"Een handige website is www.verbix.com."}]}